{"tid":825511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片：山竹過後】沙嘴懲教所營房變廢墟　職員：千祈唔好入去 (19:16)","createTime":"2018-09-17T15:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T15:52:10.000Z","uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"753d602f74ba5338f6552c0351844f81c7d5ca8e","tid":825511,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"【短片：山竹過後】沙嘴懲教所營房變廢墟　職員：千祈唔好入去 (19:16)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/07f320dd0f2bc2c6335201c6cb4c459f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F07f320dd0f2bc2c6335201c6cb4c459f.jpg&h=6f503453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖7之1 - 【山竹過後】沙嘴懲教所營房變廢墟　職員：千祈唔好入去（網上片段）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/07f416aeb1303b610e0b8076c47d9304.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F07f416aeb1303b610e0b8076c47d9304.jpg&h=dd904a44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/07f3f16dd25ab45041f3b464d2e360f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F07f3f16dd25ab45041f3b464d2e360f9.jpg&h=12e600fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/07f3d729d541b34da12351b1361c762a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F07f3d729d541b34da12351b1361c762a.jpg&h=addae4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/07f3bbc0d22c45eb94780410edb7c8e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F07f3bbc0d22c45eb94780410edb7c8e9.jpg&h=aa2c0dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180917/s00001/07f39722af2dc10bf1749b382a2180f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F07f39722af2dc10bf1749b382a2180f6.jpg&h=841ad090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n強颱風「山竹」吹襲本港期間，在多處造成嚴重破壞，除市區有唐樓外牆倒塌外，大嶼山沙嘴懲教所亦不能倖免。所內一間職員營房外牆倒塌，旁邊路面下陷，營房地基亦恐被沖毀。有職員面對儼如廢墟的營房，提醒同袍：「千祈唔好入去呀呢棟嘢！」<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：「山竹」吹散石澳情人橋　斷成數截毀了<br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳片段可見，營房外的石屎路已倒塌，地面一片泥濘，懲教署職員只能沿旁邊尚算完整的小路前進。一間營房其中一面外牆幾乎完全消失，只餘冷氣機只靠鐵架連接僅餘的外牆頂部，百葉簾及部分窗框搖搖欲墜。原放於室內的家俬雜物已被吹至一片混亂。有職員看見眼前情境，不禁嘆了一句：「打仗咩&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n旁邊另外兩間營房外的路面同樣已塌陷，現場滿目瘡痍。有懲教署職員指着其中一間營房，提醒同袍「千祈唔好入去呀呢棟嘢」，指營房地基已「真空晒，我都驚佢會冧」，有人回應要進去取回物品，之後便會離開。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署回覆《明報》查詢，指沙嘴懲教所一間職員營房在「山竹」吹襲時受破壞，其間並無懲教🇨🇳人員🇨🇳受傷。院所管方已即時安排受影響的懲教🇨🇳人員🇨🇳入住其他職員宿舍，及聯絡相關部門跟進。"},{"pid":"770733d50d90496479aae46afe7f955c1b020fa2","tid":825511,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:49:39.000Z","msg":"IS THAT KARMA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d793ddc54a086dda1ce3b98e5a37514e59322fc0","tid":825511,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"應驗中銀既沮咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}